frclib

Class FrcVisionTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • frclib.FrcOpenCVDetector<Rect[]>
      • frclib.FrcVisionTarget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    trclib.TrcVisionTask.VisionProcessor<Mat,Rect[]>

    public abstract class FrcVisionTarget
extends FrcOpenCVDetector<Rect[]>
    This class implements a Vision Targeting system that uses OpenCV. It uses a separate vision thread and will take care of thread synchronization so making the use of this class extremely simple. This class is intended to be inherited by another class that provides specific methods to process the image and to retrieve the results.
